    99→   *        (will not be used to reserve transactions)
   100→   * @param isLockHeld the {@link Predicate} used to determine if the lockID is held or not at the
   101→   *        time of invocation. If the store is used for a {@link Fate} which runs a dead
   102→   *        reservation cleaner, this should be non-null, otherwise null is fine
   103→   */
